text: Julio Jesús de las Casas is a sports shooter from Venezuela. Casas competed at the 1980 Summer Olympics and the 1984 Summer Olympics. He was born on 12 April 1945.Julio Jesús de las Casas == References == Category:1945 births Category:Living people Category:Venezuelan sport shooters Category:Olympians for Venezuela
